[src:mage-ai/introduction-overview] Don’t have a large team dedicated to Airflow?
[src:mage-ai/introduction-overview] Mage makes it easy for a single developer or small team to scale up and manage thousands of pipelines.
[src:mage-ai/introduction-overview] Every user experience and technical design decision adheres to these principles.
